OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FRain, locally heavy at first,
OL,6,Feases as it clears eastwards this
OL,7,Fmorning. Brighter conditions follow
OL,8,Fwith scattered showers. Late afternoon
OL,9,Fmost places become dry with late
OL,10,Fsunshine. Strong winds likely along
OL,11,Fthe coast this morning, then easing.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FClear spells for a time this
OL,14,Fevening, with temperatures quickly
OL,15,Ffalling. Then cloud increases with a
OL,16,Ffew showers possibly arriving, before
OL,17,Frain reaches Derbyshire late tonight.
OL,18,FAlso becoming breezy.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
