OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CSunday:FRain quickly spreads east to
OL,6,Fremaining areas, then eases to turn
OL,7,Flight and patchy by late morning, with
OL,8,Fmost places becoming dry and cloudy
OL,9,Fthrough the afternoon. Breezy and mild.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FDry
OL,12,Fand breezy with bright or sunny spells
OL,13,FMonday. Tuesday and Wednesday
OL,14,Fpredominantly cloudy with a chance of
OL,15,Fpatchy light rain or drizzle at times.
OL,16,FGenerally mild or very mild.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
